      This part is enabled only when <code>$enable-bootstrap-compatibility</code> is set to <code>true</code>. Read more about <a href={`${getVersionedDocsPath('/foundation/approach/#bootstrap-compatibility')}`}>Bootstrap compatibility</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <slot />
</details>
